!! ## Tags for POS (primary tags)

!! ### Main Word Classes

 +encl   !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = clitic to separate clitics from suffixes with identical upper form in disambiguator.cg3 (TTAAQ)
 +N      !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Noun
 +V      !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Verb
 +Pali   !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Particle-like - partikellignende
 +Conj   !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Conjunction
 +Adv    !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Adverb
 +Interj !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Interjection
 +Pron   !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Pronoun
 +Prop   !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Propernoun
 +Num    !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Numeral
 +Symbol !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = independent symbols in the text stream, like ┬ú, ÔéČ, ┬ę
 +Arab   !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = pga- brug i ~/langtech/shared-mul/src/fst/stems/telephone.lexc 



