 +Gram/HV !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Non-marked agentive Verb (used as Half-transitive)
 +Gram/Db !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Double-transitive Verb. PL tilf├Şjet 20180319
 +Gram/Exclm !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Exclamation !Flyttet fra prim├Žre tags 20180420 PL

