!! ### Grammar

 +Gram/Comp  !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Composita !S├Žrlig tag til NIQ ajor/saper/artor/nalu- konstruktioner ved transitive verber
 +Gram/Refl  !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Reflexive, reciprocal or passive !asavoq
