 +Der/vn    !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = verb to noun
 +Der/xx  !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Follows the enclitic suffix TUQ to be able to distinguish TUQ+xx from the derivational morpheme TUQ+vn in CG: qanortoq
