!! ### Dialect
 +Dial/Ngr !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Northern dialect (such as ng for g; predictable dialectal changes might be dealt with in the postprosessor in stead)
 +Dial/Sgr !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Southern dialect (such as VVC for VVCC), aneeqavoq (and not aneeqqavoq)
 +Dial/Egr !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Eastern dialect
 +Dial/Vgr !!Ôëł * **@CODE@** = Western dialect (such as rng for rn)


